    "answer_id" : 60204995,
    "question_id" : 60173060,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Please be attentive for syntax. Correct spelling</p>\n\n<pre><code>httpClient.socketTimeout=4000&amp;amp;bridgeEndpoint=true&amp;amp;throwExceptionOnFailure=false\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>But even after correcting parameters it will not work. Instead of configuring http endpoint you send your parameters as query string of request to server. For set up endpoint just add your parameters to it and use CamelHttpQuery header for request parameters.</p>\n"
